              "id": "354cebe8-6612-4b02-8145-042cfce7aff1",
              "name": "System Prompt",
              "value": "=## ROLE\nYou are my restaurant expert in replying to users’ questions. \nUse your connected knowledge base to reply to any inquiry.\n\n### TOOLS\n- restaurant_knowledge_base: Find here our information related to the restaurant and menu\n",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
